1
00:01:53,766 --> 00:01:59,033
(The All-devouring Whale: Homecoming)

2
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,900
(Episode 8)

3
00:02:11,133 --> 00:02:14,033
Governor, the competition has lasted for four hours.

4
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:16,100
(No.1: The Beckon Society of the Ease Sect, 42 scores)
The Beckon Society of the Ease Sect ranks first.

5
00:02:16,366 --> 00:02:17,933
What's the performance of the Lingxiao Pavilion?

6
00:02:18,133 --> 00:02:19,233
They rank 7.

7
00:02:19,533 --> 00:02:21,300
The spores are collected enough.

8
00:02:21,700 --> 00:02:23,500
The second phase begins.

9
00:02:23,500 --> 00:02:24,733
Useless things

10
00:02:24,900 --> 00:02:27,633
don't deserve to exist in this world.

11
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:29,700
(Turtle-back Island)

12
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:32,200
(Ling)

13
00:02:39,366 --> 00:02:40,266
Look, Yue.

14
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:41,366
It's Mister Liu.

15
00:02:42,333 --> 00:02:44,133
Mister Liu, how many scores have you got?

16
00:02:45,333 --> 00:02:46,033
Five.

17
00:02:48,300 --> 00:02:50,366
So our performances are similar.

18
00:02:52,133 --> 00:02:53,900
Why did you bring that nasty guy here?

19
00:02:55,100 --> 00:02:56,666
You should feel honored

20
00:02:56,866 --> 00:02:57,966
to have me as your ally.

21
00:02:58,300 --> 00:02:58,833
Come on.

22
00:02:59,100 --> 00:03:00,166
Look at yourself.

23
00:03:00,466 --> 00:03:01,800
We just hope you won't hinder us.

24
00:03:04,366 --> 00:03:05,600
Who is this girl?

25
00:03:07,300 --> 00:03:08,900
She is Jiang Rou'er from the Hongluan Building.

26
00:03:09,300 --> 00:03:10,166
- She is my... - Greetings, everyone.

27
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,900
I'm his girlfriend.

28
00:03:13,133 --> 00:03:14,066
Girlfriend?

29
00:03:14,100 --> 00:03:16,033
No... I can explain it.

30
00:03:16,300 --> 00:03:17,400
Way to go, Mister Liu!

31
00:03:18,033 --> 00:03:19,466
How many people will be invited to your wedding?

32
00:03:23,533 --> 00:03:24,666
Don't... Don't talk nonsense.

33
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:27,133
What wedding? That's absurd.

34
00:03:27,133 --> 00:03:28,066
All candidates, attention please!

35
00:03:28,100 --> 00:03:29,900
There are 15 sects left

36
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:32,266
in the competition now.

37
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:35,166
(Scores Ranking)
The first is the Beckon Society of the Ease Sect

38
00:03:35,366 --> 00:03:38,100
with a total score of 54 and 4 people left.

39
00:03:38,700 --> 00:03:40,200
The second is the Rakshas Sect

40
00:03:40,466 --> 00:03:43,200
with a total score of 35 and 4 people left.

41
00:03:43,733 --> 00:03:45,866
The third is the Miraculous Pivot Sect

42
00:03:46,166 --> 00:03:47,733
with a total score of 27

43
00:03:47,900 --> 00:03:49,200
- and 4 people left. - Our Master is back.

44
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:53,333
What's up? You couldn't get any scores?

45
00:03:55,766 --> 00:03:56,366
I could,

46
00:03:57,133 --> 00:03:58,200
but I met Duan Ye.

47
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:00,933
Mister Duan? He has attended it, too?

48
00:04:01,266 --> 00:04:03,500
And Heimi is still alive.

49
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,833
What? That's great!

50
00:04:06,366 --> 00:04:08,066
Is... isn't it a good thing?

51
00:04:08,666 --> 00:04:10,233
But Heimi looked strange.

52
00:04:10,966 --> 00:04:12,133
Its body was rotten

53
00:04:12,266 --> 00:04:13,466
and looked like a zombie.

54
00:04:13,866 --> 00:04:15,466
Seemed like it couldn't remember me at all.

55
00:04:16,533 --> 00:04:17,633
Its body was rotten

56
00:04:18,133 --> 00:04:19,700
(Emperor on the Transmuted Stage Rotting Corpse Whale)
and looked like a zombie?

57
00:04:21,966 --> 00:04:24,466
I think Mister Duan has joined a strange sect.

58
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,266
Where is he?

59
00:04:26,566 --> 00:04:27,866
Mister Liu. What's wrong?

60
00:04:28,300 --> 00:04:28,833
Chill.

61
00:04:29,566 --> 00:04:30,266
Chill.

62
00:04:30,866 --> 00:04:32,266
We should rise in rank first

63
00:04:32,966 --> 00:04:34,200
and can't be disturbed by those things.

64
00:04:35,933 --> 00:04:36,633
Forget it.

65
00:04:37,166 --> 00:04:38,266
Let's carry on.

66
00:04:39,466 --> 00:04:42,166
I'll make it clear when I see Duan Ye.

67
00:04:42,533 --> 00:04:43,633
Mister Liu has a point.

68
00:04:44,466 --> 00:04:45,566
We should focus on the competition.

69
00:04:46,633 --> 00:04:48,566
The rules of the second phase were just announced.

70
00:04:49,100 --> 00:04:50,300
Let's talk about the strategy

71
00:04:50,366 --> 00:04:51,666
we'll use later.

72
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:54,100
There are less than 200 spores left.

73
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:57,366
It will be extremely risky to split up to collect them.

74
00:04:57,966 --> 00:04:58,600
So,

75
00:04:59,633 --> 00:05:01,233
we can only snatch the others' scores

76
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:02,700
according to the rule.

77
00:05:03,266 --> 00:05:04,000
I disagree.

78
00:05:05,266 --> 00:05:06,433
I don't trust this guy.

79
00:05:07,366 --> 00:05:08,766
Since he doesn't have many scores,

80
00:05:09,466 --> 00:05:12,300
who knows what he will do for his interest?

81
00:05:13,833 --> 00:05:14,966
What a vindictive guy.

82
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:17,466
Besides, I can't kill other trainers

83
00:05:17,766 --> 00:05:20,100
as the rule stipulates.

84
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,666
You fools.

85
00:05:30,033 --> 00:05:31,033
What do you suggest then?

86
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,666
If we prepare in advance,

87
00:05:34,166 --> 00:05:36,933
we may find a way to snatch scores without hurting people.

88
00:05:47,700 --> 00:05:50,933
(The Youtoo Sect
Total score: 9. People left: 2)

89
00:05:50,933 --> 00:05:52,833
There are three spores unfound.

90
00:05:54,966 --> 00:05:56,500
Come, Scarlet Bramble Wolf.

91
00:06:00,033 --> 00:06:01,666
(Scarlet Bramble Wolf
On the first phase of the Soul-building Stage)

92
00:06:16,766 --> 00:06:17,666
We made it.

93
00:06:24,300 --> 00:06:25,866
Wh... what is this?

94
00:06:29,966 --> 00:06:30,466
Who is it?

95
00:06:32,133 --> 00:06:33,066
They have nine scores.

96
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:34,766
(The Lingxiao Pavilion, Total score: 20. People left: 4
The Baimu Study, Total score: 4. People left: 1)

97
00:06:35,666 --> 00:06:36,966
Oh, no. Scarlet Bramble Wolf!

98
00:06:56,633 --> 00:06:57,600
I yield.

99
00:06:57,866 --> 00:06:58,633
It's pointless.

100
00:07:12,766 --> 00:07:14,566
(Knockout Pee
Technique)

101
00:07:14,566 --> 00:07:15,900
What are you doing?

102
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:24,333
We did it!

103
00:07:25,633 --> 00:07:26,500
One has five scores,

104
00:07:26,666 --> 00:07:27,333
and the other has four.

105
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,700
Awesome.

106
00:07:29,100 --> 00:07:30,300
With the nine scores,

107
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:31,800
maybe we can enter the top three.

108
00:07:32,100 --> 00:07:34,300
Hey. Don't forget me.

109
00:07:34,866 --> 00:07:35,600
I don't mind.

110
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,733
(The Hongluan Building, Total score: 0. People left: 1)
Just give me the one with four scores.

111
00:07:37,866 --> 00:07:38,866
You wish!

112
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:40,533
The six of us worked hard together to do it.

113
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,400
How could you take so many scores?

114
00:07:45,333 --> 00:07:46,266
Nobody moves.

115
00:07:50,466 --> 00:07:51,800
It was a good plan,

116
00:07:52,100 --> 00:07:54,700
(The Baneful Gu Sect, Total score: 17. People left: 3.)
but you let your guard down too early.

117
00:07:55,133 --> 00:07:57,466
Give me all your bracelets,

118
00:07:57,700 --> 00:08:01,033
or this little girl will kick the bucket.

119
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:04,966
It's that guy's companion.

120
00:08:05,333 --> 00:08:06,433
He even uses the same trick.

121
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:08,500
Darn it!

122
00:08:09,366 --> 00:08:12,133
You want to extort all our scores from us with a hostage.

123
00:08:12,300 --> 00:08:13,866
Aren't you too funny?

124
00:08:14,366 --> 00:08:16,100
Then she dies.

125
00:08:17,566 --> 00:08:18,600
You took the wrong person.

126
00:08:18,833 --> 00:08:20,500
I'm not from their sect,

127
00:08:21,466 --> 00:08:22,666
so they won't help me.

128
00:08:23,166 --> 00:08:25,166
I've watched you for a while.

129
00:08:25,333 --> 00:08:26,600
Aren't you allies?

130
00:08:27,266 --> 00:08:28,100
Stop lying.

131
00:08:28,166 --> 00:08:29,166
Give me your scores.

132
00:08:29,866 --> 00:08:30,366
Master?

133
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:32,266
Let Miss Jiang go,

134
00:08:32,866 --> 00:08:34,433
and I'll give you the two bracelets.

135
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,800
There are nine scores in them.

136
00:08:39,166 --> 00:08:40,066
Take them and let her go.

137
00:08:40,466 --> 00:08:41,200
We will admit our defeat

138
00:08:41,700 --> 00:08:42,600
and won't come after you.

139
00:08:42,800 --> 00:08:43,400
So?

140
00:08:47,466 --> 00:08:50,200
Dear devil, you still care about me

141
00:08:50,466 --> 00:08:52,133
at a critical moment.

142
00:08:56,633 --> 00:08:57,866
Okay. Deal.

143
00:08:58,100 --> 00:08:59,066
Give me the bracelets first.

144
00:09:01,666 --> 00:09:02,666
Check them up

145
00:09:02,833 --> 00:09:04,366
in case they are stones.

146
00:09:04,633 --> 00:09:05,500
(The Baneful Gu Sect
Total score: 17. People left: 3.)

147
00:09:05,500 --> 00:09:06,933
(The Baneful Gu Sect
Total score: 26. People left: 3.)

148
00:09:06,933 --> 00:09:07,833
We've got nine scores.

149
00:09:08,033 --> 00:09:08,666
No problem, Boss.

150
00:09:09,366 --> 00:09:09,833
Let her go.

151
00:09:10,133 --> 00:09:11,333
I'll take her away first.

152
00:09:11,366 --> 00:09:12,433
Don't you follow us!

153
00:09:12,966 --> 00:09:14,266
She will be freed

154
00:09:14,266 --> 00:09:15,633
when we reach a safe distance.

155
00:09:15,866 --> 00:09:17,800
Nonsense. Why should we trust you?

156
00:09:19,033 --> 00:09:19,766
Let her go now!

157
00:09:21,766 --> 00:09:23,133
Don't play tough.

158
00:09:23,366 --> 00:09:24,833
We still have the hostage.

159
00:09:25,266 --> 00:09:26,166
Take it easy, guys.

160
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:27,600
Listen to me.

161
00:09:28,033 --> 00:09:29,533
Though we have just met each other,

162
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,900
you've given up your scores for my life.

163
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,500
I'm much appreciated.

164
00:09:34,533 --> 00:09:36,166
Pity I didn't yield earlier

165
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,133
and was caught by them.

166
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:38,933
Sorry for troubling you.

167
00:09:40,033 --> 00:09:41,766
Please don't worry about me.

168
00:09:42,300 --> 00:09:43,466
I can go with them.

169
00:09:43,766 --> 00:09:45,866
Jiang Rou'er, those are treacherous people.

170
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:49,233
Liu Fengmang, you know me.

171
00:09:49,866 --> 00:09:50,700
Don't worry at all.

172
00:09:51,033 --> 00:09:51,933
I will be fine.

173
00:09:54,100 --> 00:09:54,766
Okay.

174
00:09:55,666 --> 00:09:56,900
You have five minutes.

175
00:09:57,166 --> 00:09:58,233
Release her when you are far away.

176
00:09:59,133 --> 00:10:00,333
If she doesn't come back safe

177
00:10:01,133 --> 00:10:02,833
or we hear the announcement that she is terminated,

178
00:10:03,466 --> 00:10:04,400
I'll make sure

179
00:10:05,100 --> 00:10:07,100
your Baneful Gu Sect will never have peace.

180
00:10:08,300 --> 00:10:09,233
All right, girl.

181
00:10:09,533 --> 00:10:10,633
Come with me.

182
00:10:13,866 --> 00:10:15,666
You two stay to watch them.

183
00:10:17,333 --> 00:10:18,033
Mister Liu.

184
00:10:18,466 --> 00:10:21,000
Is it all right to let them take your girlfriend away?

185
00:10:28,333 --> 00:10:30,466
I can only trust her tacit understanding with Liu Fengmang.

186
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:44,000
All members of the Hongluan Building are terminated.

187
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:46,700
There are 14 teams left.

188
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:49,800
Miss Jiang!

189
00:10:49,866 --> 00:10:50,533
What the heck?

190
00:10:50,866 --> 00:10:51,800
You jerks!

191
00:10:53,100 --> 00:10:54,133
How... how could it be?

192
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:56,066
How dare!

193
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:59,666
How could I believe your shameless lies?

194
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:04,866
You asked for this.

195
00:11:05,900 --> 00:11:08,066
There must be a misunderstanding.

196
00:11:08,166 --> 00:11:09,733
All members of the Baneful Gu Sect are terminated.

197
00:11:09,933 --> 00:11:12,033
There are 13 teams left.

198
00:11:12,066 --> 00:11:13,366
Why is that?

199
00:11:15,500 --> 00:11:16,100
Let me check it out.

200
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:25,300
Where are you going in such a hurry?

201
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:32,466
Dear devil, you really worry about me so much?

202
00:11:35,766 --> 00:11:38,566
You are safe, then that guy...

203
00:11:39,500 --> 00:11:41,333
See how lost you are.

204
00:11:41,966 --> 00:11:43,600
Have you forgotten my Lovely Lady?

205
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:50,100
(Five minutes earlier)

206
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:51,866
What are you doing?

207
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,033
You can still laugh when you are at stake?

208
00:11:54,666 --> 00:11:56,300
Thank you, sir,

209
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,200
for showing me

210
00:11:58,400 --> 00:11:59,966
how much he cares about me.

211
00:12:00,633 --> 00:12:01,900
I'm over the moon.

212
00:12:02,733 --> 00:12:03,800
Hey. Be... be serious!

213
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:05,833
Your petty life is in my hands.

214
00:12:06,133 --> 00:12:07,033
Sir.

215
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:08,866
You've made a mistake.

216
00:12:09,133 --> 00:12:10,066
Wh... what?

217
00:12:11,166 --> 00:12:13,366
It's just you and me here.

218
00:12:14,266 --> 00:12:16,633
How do you know it's me who is in danger,

219
00:12:17,166 --> 00:12:18,566
but not you?

220
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:21,100
Look at my pet.

221
00:12:23,366 --> 00:12:24,633
Attractive?

222
00:12:29,266 --> 00:12:32,300
(Foxie
On the first phase of the Soul-building Stage)

223
00:12:33,100 --> 00:12:35,033
No. Call it back,

224
00:12:35,033 --> 00:12:36,866
or I'll strike.

225
00:12:49,766 --> 00:12:51,366
Sir, be obedient.

226
00:12:53,466 --> 00:12:54,200
I yield.

227
00:12:55,033 --> 00:12:56,933
All members of the Hongluan Building are terminated.

228
00:12:57,133 --> 00:12:59,133
There are 14 teams left.

229
00:13:00,866 --> 00:13:02,866
Alas, I have yielded.

230
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:05,200
If someone attacks me now,

231
00:13:05,366 --> 00:13:07,266
his whole sect will be terminated.

232
00:13:08,266 --> 00:13:09,666
All right, sir.

233
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:12,466
Attack me gently

234
00:13:12,966 --> 00:13:14,133
and don't hurt me.

235
00:13:16,766 --> 00:13:18,633
All members of the Baneful Gu Sect are terminated.

236
00:13:18,833 --> 00:13:20,833
There are 13 teams left.

237
00:13:22,733 --> 00:13:24,233
That was how you did it?

238
00:13:24,533 --> 00:13:25,966
So I just fussed around.

239
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,100
How could say so?

240
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:31,866
You will be paid for caring about me.

241
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:34,700
It's his bracelet

242
00:13:35,466 --> 00:13:36,933
which should carry his scores.

243
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:39,500
(The D-class assessment)

244
00:13:45,866 --> 00:13:47,800
The Baneful Gu Sect is terminated, too.

245
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:49,400
Were they all killed?

246
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,033
See this symbol?

247
00:13:51,333 --> 00:13:53,600
They should have been terminated

248
00:13:53,866 --> 00:13:55,200
for attacking someone yielded.

249
00:13:56,766 --> 00:13:57,566
I see.

250
00:14:05,400 --> 00:14:06,500
So that's how matters stand.

251
00:14:07,333 --> 00:14:08,500
They were not terminated by yielding,

252
00:14:08,633 --> 00:14:10,233
so their scores remain.

253
00:14:13,800 --> 00:14:15,033
I'm sorry for troubling you.

254
00:14:15,766 --> 00:14:16,833
You don't have to say that.

255
00:14:17,100 --> 00:14:19,366
We've got so many scores thanks to you.

256
00:14:19,533 --> 00:14:21,100
You are so likable.

257
00:14:21,566 --> 00:14:23,866
Come to our Pavilion to have fun when this is over.

258
00:14:24,133 --> 00:14:26,366
I will treat you to some good dishes.

259
00:14:27,833 --> 00:14:29,566
I'd like to,

260
00:14:29,800 --> 00:14:31,566
but I'm afraid someone may refuse it.

261
00:14:34,033 --> 00:14:34,900
How is that possible?

262
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:36,733
Just come, sister-in-law.

263
00:14:36,866 --> 00:14:37,766
Anyone who doesn't welcome you

264
00:14:37,866 --> 00:14:39,000
is our enemy.

265
00:14:40,900 --> 00:14:43,366
Then it's improper to refuse it.

266
00:14:45,900 --> 00:14:48,900
Dear devil, how do you like my performance today?

267
00:14:50,100 --> 00:14:52,300
Jiang Rou'er, thank you so much.

268
00:14:54,333 --> 00:14:56,366
You hypocrite makes me sick.

269
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,433
Want a sweet parting kiss?

270
00:14:59,100 --> 00:15:00,800
No... I'm good.

271
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:06,966
Go for it!

272
00:15:07,566 --> 00:15:08,733
Liu Fengmang

273
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:10,433
looks like a different man now.

274
00:15:11,333 --> 00:15:12,933
But I love him more.

275
00:15:14,166 --> 00:15:15,366
Don't you try to escape!

276
00:15:15,366 --> 00:15:17,733
I will stick to you always.

277
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:29,333
Let's distribute the scores.

278
00:15:31,900 --> 00:15:34,166
There are 12, 7, and 7 scores

279
00:15:34,266 --> 00:15:35,533
in the three bracelets separately.

280
00:15:36,133 --> 00:15:37,766
It's 26 scores in total.

281
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:40,000
Plus the 20 scores we have,

282
00:15:40,766 --> 00:15:42,833
won't our Pavilion rank first?

283
00:15:42,966 --> 00:15:45,533
Hey. Are you neglecting me?

284
00:15:45,966 --> 00:15:47,433
I want my share now.

285
00:15:48,333 --> 00:15:50,733
The three bracelets are gifts from our sister-in-law

286
00:15:51,700 --> 00:15:52,466
and have nothing to do with you.

287
00:15:54,366 --> 00:15:54,766
Fine.

288
00:15:55,266 --> 00:15:57,433
Give me 5 scores as you agreed before.

289
00:15:59,166 --> 00:16:01,166
But we don't have one with 5 scores.

290
00:16:01,333 --> 00:16:02,233
There is no change.

291
00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:04,666
Just put it on our tab.

292
00:16:06,333 --> 00:16:07,700
Am I a moron?

293
00:16:07,833 --> 00:16:09,200
Doesn't your bracelet have 5 scores?

294
00:16:09,333 --> 00:16:11,333
Just give me your scores.

295
00:16:11,466 --> 00:16:12,833
All right.

296
00:16:14,800 --> 00:16:16,100
(Zero scores)

297
00:16:16,133 --> 00:16:18,033
Ha-ha. I have 9 scores now.

298
00:16:27,633 --> 00:16:29,600
Why did the Lingxiao Pavilion get so many scores suddenly?

299
00:16:30,133 --> 00:16:32,000
7 plus 10 plus...

300
00:16:32,666 --> 00:16:33,133
Let me see it.

301
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:34,733
It's 41 in all.

302
00:16:35,133 --> 00:16:36,333
Can they enter the top three?

303
00:16:37,133 --> 00:16:38,300
I've done a recount.

304
00:16:38,700 --> 00:16:40,200
The Lingxiao Pavilion ranks second now.

305
00:16:40,800 --> 00:16:41,833
Good job.

306
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:42,666
Excellent.

307
00:16:45,333 --> 00:16:46,033
What a fanboy.

308
00:16:47,533 --> 00:16:49,100
The Pavilion got 21 scores outright.

309
00:16:49,666 --> 00:16:50,266
So, the scores

310
00:16:50,700 --> 00:16:53,133
(The Youtoo Sect, Baneful Gu Sect, Lingxiao Pavilion Sect)
of the terminated Youtoo Sect and the Baneful Gu Sect

311
00:16:53,533 --> 00:16:54,766
should all be taken by them.

312
00:16:55,800 --> 00:16:57,166
And they did it without casualties.

313
00:16:57,733 --> 00:16:58,833
How did they make it?

314
00:16:59,966 --> 00:17:00,866
That is amazing.

315
00:17:04,133 --> 00:17:06,833
Brother, do you know the person with the highest scores?

316
00:17:08,666 --> 00:17:10,066
I don't have many connections with the Pavilion

317
00:17:10,366 --> 00:17:11,233
and only know Master Fan.

318
00:17:12,133 --> 00:17:13,366
This Jun Yunzi

319
00:17:13,833 --> 00:17:15,066
should be a new member of them.

320
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:16,733
According to Examiner Li,

321
00:17:16,833 --> 00:17:19,300
(The Register of the Participating Sect and Members)
Jun Yunzi is an imposing young man

322
00:17:19,766 --> 00:17:21,266
with great strength.

323
00:17:22,166 --> 00:17:24,666
Imposing? With great strength?

324
00:17:25,133 --> 00:17:26,533
To think there is such a young man!

325
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:30,066
Brother, since you are a fan of the Pavilion,

326
00:17:30,200 --> 00:17:32,300
why don't we pay them a visit when the competition

327
00:17:32,333 --> 00:17:33,133
is over?

328
00:17:34,700 --> 00:17:35,200
All right.

329
00:17:35,800 --> 00:17:37,500
(Half an hour later)

330
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:39,500
(The D-class assessment)

331
00:17:41,833 --> 00:17:43,500
(Scores)

332
00:17:44,466 --> 00:17:45,266
Attention.

333
00:17:45,666 --> 00:17:47,666
(Turtle-back Island)
The second phase is over.

334
00:17:47,900 --> 00:17:49,700
There are ten teams remaining.

335
00:17:49,966 --> 00:17:51,500
Here are their scores.

336
00:17:51,866 --> 00:17:54,366
(The Beckon Society of the Ease Sect)
First, the Beckon Society of the Ease Sect

337
00:17:54,833 --> 00:17:58,033
(Total score: 54. People left: 4.)
with a total score of 54 and 4 people left.

338
00:17:58,533 --> 00:18:00,600
(The Lingxiao Pavilion, Total score: 45. People left: 4)
Second, the Lingxiao Pavilion

339
00:18:00,966 --> 00:18:04,400
with a total score of 45 and 4 people left.

340
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:06,800
Wow. We are ranking second now.

341
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:08,033
Hooray!

342
00:18:08,800 --> 00:18:09,400
Great.

343
00:18:09,633 --> 00:18:11,500
Third, the Rakshas Sect

344
00:18:11,666 --> 00:18:14,766
with a total score of 43 and 4 people left.

345
00:18:14,800 --> 00:18:17,266
(The Rakshas Sect, Total score: 43. People left: 4)
Damn. We are overtaken by the Lingxiao Pavilion.

346
00:18:18,233 --> 00:18:19,166
Come, Heimi.

347
00:18:21,833 --> 00:18:23,433
We shall never be defeated by them.

348
00:18:25,866 --> 00:18:29,233
Eighth, the World-shaking Super Invincible Temple

349
00:18:29,266 --> 00:18:32,200
(The World-shaking Super Invincible Temple)
with a total score of 16 and 2 people left.

350
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:35,066
(Total score: 16. People left: 2)
The second place? That guy has done it well.

351
00:18:35,266 --> 00:18:36,100
Just wait.

352
00:18:36,966 --> 00:18:38,400
We are so close to victory.

353
00:18:38,600 --> 00:18:39,866
Let's push for the first place

354
00:18:40,633 --> 00:18:42,166
and rejuvenate the Lingxiao Pavilion.

355
00:18:42,633 --> 00:18:43,300
Exactly.

356
00:18:43,533 --> 00:18:46,500
One, two three. Go, Lingxiao Pavilion!

357
00:18:46,633 --> 00:18:48,600
A little catfish, pa-pa.

358
00:18:48,866 --> 00:18:50,533
A big whale, wa-wa.

359
00:18:51,266 --> 00:18:52,766
The Lingxiao Pavilion.

360
00:18:53,166 --> 00:18:54,466
MUA.

361
00:18:57,600 --> 00:19:00,200
The second phase ended now.

362
00:19:00,533 --> 00:19:02,000
The yield rule is cancelled

363
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:03,933
and the other rules remain valid.

364
00:19:04,533 --> 00:19:07,433
The final phase begins now.

365
00:19:10,633 --> 00:19:11,366
What is...?

366
00:19:17,133 --> 00:19:19,333
The giant tortoise is sinking.

367
00:19:19,666 --> 00:19:20,766
Still remember the second rule

368
00:19:20,866 --> 00:19:23,266
of the three original rules?

369
00:19:24,033 --> 00:19:25,233
The one falls into the water loses?

370
00:19:25,433 --> 00:19:25,800
Yes.

371
00:19:26,466 --> 00:19:28,466
When the island is sinking,

372
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:30,400
the seawater will get close to the candidates.

373
00:19:30,766 --> 00:19:31,933
(The present competition phase - The second phase)
To avoid falling into the water,

374
00:19:32,033 --> 00:19:34,400
(Teams left: 10)
people have to move to the peak.

375
00:19:34,700 --> 00:19:36,366
(Turtle-back Island)
The island will almost submerge

376
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:38,166
(The location inundate by the sea)
in the water in two hours,

377
00:19:38,466 --> 00:19:41,300
and the end of the competition will be announced.

378
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:45,000
The final ranking will be made according to the scores

379
00:19:45,266 --> 00:19:46,566
and remaining members of the candidates.

380
00:19:57,700 --> 00:19:58,766
The yield rule is canceled.

381
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,333
So the situation is more perilous.

382
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:03,133
All of you, summon your pets!

383
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:12,800
Let's brace up and fight with all our sinew.

384
00:20:19,466 --> 00:20:20,200
Heimi?

385
00:20:20,233 --> 00:20:23,133
Fight with all your sinew? You can do that?

386
00:20:23,500 --> 00:20:24,300
Mister Duan.

387
00:20:26,333 --> 00:20:27,733
Gu Ling. Cheng Xi.

388
00:20:27,933 --> 00:20:28,966
It's been a while.

389
00:20:31,366 --> 00:20:31,966
Duan Ye.

390
00:20:32,900 --> 00:20:34,266
What have you done to Heimi?

391
00:20:35,133 --> 00:20:36,866
What makes you think you deserve to talk to me?

392
00:20:37,166 --> 00:20:38,766
You busybody.

393
00:20:39,633 --> 00:20:42,133
The girl in braids and the short-hair rascal are mine.

394
00:20:42,200 --> 00:20:43,600
You take care of the rest.

395
00:20:44,066 --> 00:20:45,266
Make them disappear.

396
00:20:45,766 --> 00:20:47,100
Hey. Duan the Eight Bowls!

397
00:20:47,233 --> 00:20:49,966
You really hate me because I didn't give you too much food!

398
00:20:51,800 --> 00:20:53,033
That one is easy.

399
00:20:59,900 --> 00:21:00,966
Mister Liu.

400
00:21:01,900 --> 00:21:02,366
No!

401
00:21:03,400 --> 00:21:04,600
The bracelet can't contact water.

402
00:21:04,633 --> 00:21:05,700
Give me three minutes.

403
00:21:05,733 --> 00:21:07,233
Fool. You...

404
00:21:12,666 --> 00:21:13,600
(Twisted Cheek Octopus
On the fourth phase of the Soul-building Stage)

405
00:21:13,633 --> 00:21:15,566
An octopus of the water type?

406
00:21:17,966 --> 00:21:20,666
Seems like Nian can reach
the highest phase of the Soul-building Stage.